 scripting history of scripting and use of scripting languages to webpages.","Able to use HTML5 Elements and differentiate with HTML.","Able to apply style sheet and JavaScript logic on webpage.","Build a dynamic web page using JavaScript & Ajax.","Able to write a script for webpage using PHP."}	{"Jeffrey C. Jackson, \\"Web Technologies - A Computer Science Perspective\\", Pearson Education.","Rasmus Lerdorf and Levin Tatroe, “Programming PHP”, O’Reilly, Third Edition.","Chris Bates, Web Programming – Building Intranet Applications, 3rd Edition, Wiley Publications, 2009.","The World of Scripting Languages, David Barron, Wiley Publications.","Web Programming, building internet applications, Chris Bates 2nd Edition, WILEY.","Beginning JavaScript with Dom scripting and AJAX, Russ Ferguson, Christian Heilmann, Apress."}	{}	{}	2025
