126	Revised Midsem Schedule	The Odd Semester mid-semester examinations have been postponed due to the upcoming Confluence event, which is scheduled to take place on campus in the coming days. Confluence is a large-scale academic and cultural gathering that requires extensive logistical arrangements, including the allocation of examination halls, classrooms, auditoriums, technical resources, and administrative staff. In order to ensure the smooth and successful conduct of this event, it has been decided by the concerned authorities to reschedule the mid-semester examinations.\n\nThe primary objective behind this decision is to avoid any clashes between academic activities and event-related arrangements, thereby minimizing inconvenience to students, faculty members, and administrative personnel. Conducting examinations alongside a major event could lead to disruptions such as limited space availability, scheduling conflicts, and increased operational challenges. By postponing the examinations, the institution aims to provide a more conducive and stress-free environment for students to perform to the best of their abilities.\n\nStudents are advised not to panic or feel anxious regarding this change. The revised examination schedule will be announced shortly through official channels after careful consideration, ensuring adequate preparation time for all students. Until then, students are encouraged to continue their academic preparation and stay updated by regularly checking official notifications and emails.\n\nThe administration appreciates the cooperation and understanding of all stakeholders and regrets any inconvenience caused due to this postponement. Further updates will be communicated in a timely manner.	2024-09-29 00:00:00	2026-01-29 07:29:11.743	\N	{https://isac-nitkkr-public.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/isaac-s3-images/slideshow/image02.jpg,https://isac-nitkkr-public.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/isaac-s3-images/slideshow/image02.jpg,https://isac-nitkkr-public.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/isaac-s3-images/slideshow/image02.jpg,https://isac-nitkkr-public.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/isaac-s3-images/slideshow/image02.jpg}	{workshop,academic}	\N
